          PACK      DEFPATH,SP30,SP30
          CLOSE     FINDFILE
          MOVE      ZERO,OVRCD
          TRAP      OVERCOND IF IO
          OPEN      FINDFILE,"temp"
          TRAPCLR   IO
          BRANCH    OVRCD,DEFT3000
